@startuml Sequence_Tchat
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.8
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #1a3c5e
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #EBF3FB
skinparam sequenceParticipantFontStyle bold
skinparam sequenceParticipantFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #aaaaaa
skinparam sequenceGroupBorderColor #555555
skinparam sequenceGroupBackgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam sequenceGroupFontColor #333333
skinparam noteBorderColor #e6a817
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF8E1
skinparam ArrowColor #1a3c5e
skinparam roundCorner 6
skinparam padding 5
title <b>Diagramme de séquence — Envoi d'un message de tchat\nYour Car Your Way</b>

actor "Client A\n(navigateur)" as CA #EBF3FB
participant "Daphne / Channels\nChatConsumer" as CHAN #E8F5E9
participant "Redis\nChannel Layer" as REDIS #FCE4EC
database "PostgreSQL" as PG #FFF8E1
actor "Client B\n(navigateur)" as CB #EDE9FE

== ① Connexion initiale ==

CA -> CHAN : WebSocket connect\nwss://host/ws/chat/support-123/
activate CHAN
CHAN -> REDIS : group_add("chat_support-123", channel_name)
activate REDIS
REDIS --> CHAN : OK
deactivate REDIS
CHAN -> PG : SELECT * FROM chat_message\nWHERE room_id = 123\nORDER BY sent_at DESC LIMIT 50
activate PG
PG --> CHAN : 50 derniers messages
deactivate PG
CHAN --> CA : WS accepted + historique messages
deactivate CHAN

== ② Envoi d'un message ==

CA -> CHAN : WS send\n**{ "message": "Bonjour, j'ai un problème\navec ma réservation #456." }**
activate CHAN

note right of CHAN
  Vérification :
  - utilisateur authentifié ?
  - message non vide ?
  - longueur ≤ 2000 caractères ?
end note

== ③ Persistance en base ==

CHAN -> PG : INSERT INTO chat_message\n(room_id, author_id, content, sent_at)
activate PG
PG --> CHAN : message_id=789, sent_at=2026-04-25T14:32:10
deactivate PG

== ④ Diffusion temps réel ==

CHAN -> REDIS : group_send("chat_support-123",\n{ type: "chat_message", message, author, sent_at })
activate REDIS
REDIS --> CHAN : dispatch → chat_message() [Client A]
REDIS --> CB : dispatch → chat_message() [Client B]
deactivate REDIS

== ⑤ Réception et affichage ==

CHAN --> CA : WS message\n{ message, author: "alice", sent_at, message_id }
deactivate CHAN
CB --> CB : Affichage du message\ndans l'interface

note over CA, CB
  <b>Latence totale observée : &lt; 500 ms</b>
  Les étapes ③ ④ ⑤ sont exécutées de façon asynchrone
  grâce à async/await (Django Channels ASGI)
end note

== ⑥ Déconnexion ==

CA -> CHAN : WebSocket close
activate CHAN
CHAN -> REDIS : group_discard("chat_support-123", channel_name)
activate REDIS
REDIS --> CHAN : OK
deactivate REDIS
deactivate CHAN
@enduml
